        "content": "<p>pchickey <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12913#issuecomment-4165905643\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12913\">issue #12913</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Behavior on macos 15 is similar but not identical: </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hickey</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">KVKD0WG7VF</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">repro_12913</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">opt</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">wasi</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">sdk</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">32.0</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">arm64</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">macos</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">wasm32</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">wasip1</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">clang</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">test_fifo_seek</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">test_fifo_seek</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wasm</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hickey</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">KVKD0WG7VF</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">repro_12913</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mkdir</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tmp</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hickey</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">KVKD0WG7VF</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">repro_12913</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">echo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"hello\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tmp</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">fifo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">22418</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">done</span><span class=\"w\">       </span><span class=\"n\">echo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"hello\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tmp</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">fifo</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hickey</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">KVKD0WG7VF</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">repro_12913</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">wasmtime</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">run</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">--</span><span class=\"n\">dir</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tmp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">test_fifo_seek</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wasm</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tmp</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">fifo</span>\n<span class=\"n\">ftell</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n<span class=\"n\">fseek</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">SEEK_END</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n<span class=\"n\">ftell</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">after</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">SEEK_END</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>",
